biography: For more than ten years, Clemens Hübner has been working at the interface between software and security. After roles as a software developer and in penetration testing, he joined inovex in 2018 as a software security engineer. Today, he supports development projects at the conception and implementation level and is a trainer both in-house and for clients. He advises on secure development processes and DevSecOps. As speaker, he is invited to national and international conferences.
